In the MATTER OF Queen E. PAYTON, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 007752001) D-23 September Term 2017
080206 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2018

ORDER

The Disciplinary Review Board having filed with the Court its decision in DRB 17-132, concluding that QUEEN E. PAYTON of MOUNT LAUREL , who was admitted to the bar of this State in 2001, should not be disciplined for violating RPC 1.15(d) and Rule 1:21-6 (recordkeeping violations), based on her history and mitigation evidence presented to the Board, and good cause appearing;

It is ORDERED that no discipline be imposed on QUEEN E. PAYTON in this matter.
